{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/ironcore\/swiftuicore\/verticalalignment\/firstline"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/IronCore\/documentation\/IronCore\/SwiftUICore\/VerticalAlignment\/firstLine","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","externalID":"s:7SwiftUI17VerticalAlignmentV8IronCoreE9firstLineACvpZ","title":"firstLine","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"static"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"firstLine"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI17VerticalAlignmentV","text":"VerticalAlignment"}],"roleHeading":"Type Property","modules":[{"relatedModules":["SwiftUICore"],"name":"IronCore"}],"extendedModule":"SwiftUICore","symbolKind":"property"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Aligns content to the center of the first line of text."}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/IronCore\/documentation\/IronCore","doc:\/\/IronCore\/documentation\/IronCore\/SwiftUICore","doc:\/\/IronCore\/documentation\/IronCore\/SwiftUICore\/VerticalAlignment"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"static","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"firstLine","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"VerticalAlignment","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI17VerticalAlignmentV"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This alignment is analogous to the default behavior of SwiftUI’s ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Label"},{"text":", where","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the icon is vertically centered with the first line of the label text. Unlike","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Label"},{"text":", this alignment can be used with any view, any spacing, and any number","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of subviews.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The alignment uses SwiftUI’s text baseline alignment guides to calculate the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"center of the first line. It works by finding the difference between the first","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and last text baselines, then computing the midpoint of the remaining height.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Usage","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Usage"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Use ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".firstLine"},{"text":" as the alignment parameter for ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"HStack"},{"text":":","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["HStack(alignment: .firstLine, spacing: 12) {","  Image(systemName: \"star.fill\")","    .foregroundStyle(.yellow)","  VStack(alignment: .leading) {","    Text(\"First Line\")","      .font(.headline)","    Text(\"Second Line\")","    Text(\"Third Line\")","  }","}"]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The star icon will be vertically centered with “First Line”, regardless of how","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"many additional lines of text appear below.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Common-Use-Cases","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Common Use Cases"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Timeline entries","type":"text"}]},{"text":": Align node indicators with the first line of event descriptions","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"List items","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Align icons or checkboxes with the first line of multiline labels"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Form fields","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Align validation icons with the first line of error messages","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Comments\/Reviews","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Align avatars with the first line of comment text"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"How It Works","anchor":"How-It-Works"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The alignment calculates:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The height after the first line: "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"lastTextBaseline - firstTextBaseline"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The height of the first line: ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"totalHeight - heightAfterFirstLine"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The center point: "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"heightOfFirstLine \/ 2"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"orderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This positions the alignment guide at the vertical center of the first line of text."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://IronCore/documentation/IronCore":{"kind":"symbol","title":"IronCore","abstract":[{"text":"Foundation module providing theming, tokens, and accessibility utilities.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/IronCore\/documentation\/IronCore","role":"collection","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/ironcore"},"doc://IronCore/documentation/IronCore/SwiftUICore":{"type":"topic","role":"collection","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/IronCore\/documentation\/IronCore\/SwiftUICore","title":"SwiftUICore","url":"\/documentation\/ironcore\/swiftuicore","kind":"symbol"},"doc://IronCore/documentat